## Service module pattern (always follow this)
Each service file exports a class with async methods.
Services never import from routers. Routers import from services only.
Example:
  class AuthService:
      async def create_user(self, data: UserCreate) -> UserResponse: ...
      async def authenticate(self, email: str, password: str) -> TokenResponse: ...

## Vitals thresholds (default, patient-configurable)
Heart rate: warn >100, alert >130, critical >180, warn <50, critical <40
SpO2: warn <94%, critical <88%
Systolic BP: warn >140, critical >180, warn <90, critical <80
Diastolic BP: warn >90, critical >120, warn <60, critical <50

## Alert escalation levels
Level 1: In-app notification (immediate)
Level 2: In-app red alert + unacknowledged for 60s
Level 3: Fast2SMS to patient (unacknowledged for 120s)
Level 4: Fast2SMS to caregiver (unacknowledged for 180s)
Level 5: Critical вЂ” immediate SMS to all contacts + show emergency button

## AI model usage
Primary (health queries, symptom analysis): BioMistral via Ollama
  model name: "biomistral" or "medllama2"
Fallback / translation / intent: Llama 3.2 via Ollama
  model name: "llama3.2"
Always stream responses when possible.
Always include confidence check вЂ” if response contains uncertainty markers, add escalation note.

## Voice pipeline
STT: faster-whisper model="small" device="cuda" (RTX 4060)
VAD: silero-vad вЂ” detect speech start/end, no manual button needed
TTS: Coqui TTS вЂ” offline Hindi model primary, gTTS fallback when online
Intent classification: Llama 3.2 вЂ” classify as navigation/health_query/emergency
Emergency keywords: ["а¤®а¤¦а¤¦", "help", "emergency", "bachao", "а¤¬а¤ља¤ѕа¤“"] вЂ” bypass all pipeline

## Languages supported
Hindi, English, Marathi, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, Gujarati, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi
Language code mapping same as Arogyamitra's translations.py

## Key patterns from Arogyamitra to preserve
- Multi-role system: Patient / Doctor / Caregiver
- get_text(key, language) function for all UI strings
- Health profile with: blood_type, height, weight, allergies, chronic_conditions, medications
- WhatsApp share URL generation
- Emergency contacts: ambulance=102, police=100, emergency=112

## What NOT to port from Arogyamitra
- Streamlit UI code (app.py) вЂ” do not port, rebuild in React
- Flat JSON file storage вЂ” use SQLite + InfluxDB instead
- gTTS-only TTS вЂ” replace with Coqui + gTTS fallback
- Raw Llama 3 вЂ” replace with BioMistral
- Google Fit API вЂ” replace with Health Connect API